===
Git
===

BASIC WORKFLOW:
==============
    $ # create a remote branch
    $ mkdir arbitrator
    $ cd arbitrator
    $ git init
    $ git remote add origin 192.168.1.3:/usr/local/git_root/arbitrator-project.git
    $ git remote -v
    $ git pull origin master
    $ git log

    $ # add/edit a file
    $ git add docs/subversion # git add -A
    $ git status
    $ git commit
    $ git push origin master

    $ # somewhere else...
    $ git pull origin master


REFERENCES:
==========
